## components Datasheets 

This folder contains the datasheets for all major electronic components used in the autonomous robot project.Each datasheet provides essential technical information such as:

-Electrical characteristics

-Pin configurations

-Operating voltages

-Timing diagrams

-Mechanical dimensions

-Usage guidelines

These documents are critical for correct system design, wiring, and integration of the robot’s hardware components.


## Repository Structure

| File/Folder Name                          | Description                                         |
|-------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------|
| Arduino_Uno_Datasheet.PDF                 | Datasheet for Arduino Uno microcontroller board     |
| IR_Sensor-Datasheet.pdf                   | Datasheet for IR sensor used in line detection      |
| L298N Motor Driver Datasheet.pdf          | Datasheet for L298N motor driver IC                 |
| Ultra_Sonic_Sensor(4-pins)_Datasheet.pdf  | Datasheet for HC‑SR04 ultrasonic distance sensor    |
| README                                    | Documentation describing component datasheets usage |


